# Copied to out/.assetsignore by Next. Tells `wrangler deploy` (Workers Static
# Assets) to skip files from the upload. The onnxruntime-web JSEP/WebGPU wasm is
# ~26 MB — over Cloudflare's 25 MiB per-file limit — and is loaded from a CDN at
# runtime instead (see lib/config.ts ORT_WASM_BASE_URL). Excluding it here keeps
# the deploy under the limit; nothing requests the local copy.
_next/static/media/*.wasm
